  ('Sate Ayam', 'Traditional Indonesian grilled chicken skewers', 'Chicken, soy sauce, kecap manis, garlic, shallots, lemongrass, salt, pepper', 'Marinate the chicken with soy sauce, kecap manis, minced garlic, minced shallots, minced lemongrass, salt, and pepper. Skewer the marinated chicken. Grill the skewered chicken until cooked through.', 'hdata:image/jpeg;base64,'),
