  ('Martabak Manis', 'Indonesian sweet thick pancake', 'Flour, yeast, sugar, coconut milk, condensed milk, chocolate sprinkles/cheese/peanuts', 'Mix flour, yeast, sugar, and coconut milk into a batter. Let it rest until it doubles in size. Pour the batter onto a hot greased pan. Add your choice of fillings (chocolate sprinkles, cheese, peanuts). Fold the pancake and cook until golden brown on both sides.', 'data:image/jpeg;base64,'),
